
Authentication Endpoints:
- /auth/users/ (POST: register)
- /auth/users/me/ (GET: current user)
- /auth/jwt/create/ (POST: obtain JWT tokens)
- /auth/jwt/refresh/ (POST: refresh access token)
- /auth/jwt/verify/ (POST: verify token)


New Authentication Endpoints:
http://localhost:8000/accounts/submit-email/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/verify-email/<token>/ (GET)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/complete-registration/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/login/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/forgot-password/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/reset-password/<uuid:token>/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/change-password/ (POST)



http://localhost:8000/accounts/create-doctor-profile/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-doctors/<int:id>/ (GET)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-doctors/ (GET)

http://localhost:8000/accounts/create-patient-profile/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-patients/ (GET)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-patients/<int:id>/ (GET)

http://localhost:8000/accounts/create-pharmacy-profile/ (POST)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-pharmacy-stores/ (GET)
http://localhost:8000/accounts/get-pharmacy-stores/<int:id>/ (GET)



